<subSubSection id="6E8C6532290B3272FF7E2F99FC4DD9D4" pageId="1" pageNumber="251" type="description">
<paragraph id="262936B9290B3272FF7E2F99FEEDDBB9" blockId="1.[151,506,1184,1247]" box="[151,361,1220,1247]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">
<figureCitation id="BEAD2A3C290B3272FF7E2F99FE93DBB8" box="[151,279,1220,1247]" captionStart="FIGURES 10–18" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[160,1428,194,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-22@3.[160,1428,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 10–18. Longicornus brevispinus Fang &amp; Xing, 2019: 10. ♂, dorsal view; 11. ♂, lateral view; 12. ♂,face; Longicornus grossus sp. nov.: 13. ♂, dorsal view; 14. ♂, lateral view; 15. ♂,face; Longicornus longus Xing &amp; Li: 16. ♂, dorsal view; 17. ♂, lateral view; 18. ♂,face." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500915" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500915/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Figs 13–15</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="BEAD2A3C290B3272FECB2F99FEEDDBB9" box="[290,361,1220,1246]" captionStart-0="FIGURES 29–35" captionStart-1="FIGURES 36–41" captionStartId-0="4.[151,264,1966,1990]" captionStartId-1="5.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox-0="[237,1353,1051,1937]" captionTargetBox-1="[187,1399,198,1903]" captionTargetId-0="figure-88@4.[231,1357,1043,1943]" captionTargetId-1="figure-22@5.[172,1416,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId-0="4" captionTargetPageId-1="5" captionText-0="FIGURES 29–35. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 29. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 30. Valve, ventral view; 31. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 32. Aedeagus, lateral view; 33. Aedeagus, ventral view; 34. Connective, dorsal view; 35. Style, dorsal view." captionText-1="FIGURES 36–41. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 36. Genital capsule, lateral view; 37. Female seventh sternite, ventral view; 38. First valvula, lateral view; 39. Detail of sculptures of first valvula; 40. Second valvula, lateral view; 41. Detail of sculptures of second valaula." figureDoi-0="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500919" figureDoi-1="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500921" httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/6500919/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/6500921/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">29–41</figureCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="262936B9290B3272FF7E2E51FDD8DA09" blockId="1.[151,1437,1292,1930]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">
<emphasis id="14E2EAAB290B3272FF7E2E51FEADDA41" bold="true" box="[151,297,1292,1318]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Description.</emphasis>
Body short, robust and fuscous (
<figureCitation id="BEAD2A3C290B3272FD7E2E51FD6EDA41" box="[663,746,1292,1318]" captionStart="FIGURES 10–18" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[160,1428,194,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-22@3.[160,1428,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 10–18. Longicornus brevispinus Fang &amp; Xing, 2019: 10. ♂, dorsal view; 11. ♂, lateral view; 12. ♂,face; Longicornus grossus sp. nov.: 13. ♂, dorsal view; 14. ♂, lateral view; 15. ♂,face; Longicornus longus Xing &amp; Li: 16. ♂, dorsal view; 17. ♂, lateral view; 18. ♂,face." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500915" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500915/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Fig. 13</figureCitation>
). Vertex with paired irregular dark brown bands. Face marked with irregular yellowish brown lateral stripe (
<figureCitation id="BEAD2A3C290B3272FD4C2E6DFD7FDA2C" box="[677,763,1328,1355]" captionStart="FIGURES 10–18" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[160,1428,194,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-22@3.[160,1428,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 10–18. Longicornus brevispinus Fang &amp; Xing, 2019: 10. ♂, dorsal view; 11. ♂, lateral view; 12. ♂,face; Longicornus grossus sp. nov.: 13. ♂, dorsal view; 14. ♂, lateral view; 15. ♂,face; Longicornus longus Xing &amp; Li: 16. ♂, dorsal view; 17. ♂, lateral view; 18. ♂,face." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500915" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500915/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Fig. 15</figureCitation>
). Forewing dark brown, with scatered hyaline areas (Figs. 13,14). Legs brownish, with dark bands.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="262936B9290B3272FF2E2E25FD21DAF5" blockId="1.[151,1437,1292,1930]" box="[199,677,1400,1427]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">External features as in generic description.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="262936B9290B3272FF2E2EC1FB06DA99" blockId="1.[151,1437,1292,1930]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">
<emphasis id="14E2EAAB290B3272FF2E2EC1FEF7DAD1" box="[199,371,1436,1462]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Male genitalia.</emphasis>
Subgenital plate with 6 setae along lateral margin (
<figureCitation id="BEAD2A3C290B3272FC5C2EC1FB8DDAD1" box="[949,1033,1436,1462]" captionStart="FIGURES 29–35" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1966,1990]" captionTargetBox="[237,1353,1051,1937]" captionTargetId="figure-88@4.[231,1357,1043,1943]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 29–35. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 29. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 30. Valve, ventral view; 31. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 32. Aedeagus, lateral view; 33. Aedeagus, ventral view; 34. Connective, dorsal view; 35. Style, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500919" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500919/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Fig. 31</figureCitation>
). Aedeagal shaft short and robust in ventral view, aedeagus with pair of furcate processes with one branch approximately as long as shaft and extended distad, other branch shorter than half length of shaft and extended posterad (
<figureCitation id="BEAD2A3C290B3272FC042EB9FBF1DA99" box="[1005,1141,1508,1534]" captionStart="FIGURES 29–35" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1966,1990]" captionTargetBox="[237,1353,1051,1937]" captionTargetId="figure-88@4.[231,1357,1043,1943]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 29–35. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 29. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 30. Valve, ventral view; 31. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 32. Aedeagus, lateral view; 33. Aedeagus, ventral view; 34. Connective, dorsal view; 35. Style, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500919" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500919/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Figs. 32, 33</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="262936B9290B3272FF392D55FD21D9E9" blockId="1.[151,1437,1292,1930]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">
Female seventh sternite approximately as long as broad at base, caudal margin medially produced (
<figureCitation id="BEAD2A3C290B3272FAD32D55FA14D945" box="[1338,1424,1544,1570]" captionStart="FIGURES 36–41" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[187,1399,198,1903]" captionTargetId="figure-22@5.[172,1416,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 36–41. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 36. Genital capsule, lateral view; 37. Female seventh sternite, ventral view; 38. First valvula, lateral view; 39. Detail of sculptures of first valvula; 40. Second valvula, lateral view; 41. Detail of sculptures of second valaula." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500921" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500921/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Fig. 37</figureCitation>
). Female pygofer with ventroposterior margin slightly incurved. (
<figureCitation id="BEAD2A3C290B3272FC972D71FC52D920" box="[894,982,1580,1607]" captionStart="FIGURES 36–41" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[187,1399,198,1903]" captionTargetId="figure-22@5.[172,1416,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 36–41. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 36. Genital capsule, lateral view; 37. Female seventh sternite, ventral view; 38. First valvula, lateral view; 39. Detail of sculptures of first valvula; 40. Second valvula, lateral view; 41. Detail of sculptures of second valaula." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500921" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500921/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Fig. 36</figureCitation>
). First valvulae with obscure reticulate sculpture dorsally and scale-like sculpture ventrally (
<figureCitation id="BEAD2A3C290B3272FD002D0DFCF7D90D" box="[745,883,1616,1642]" captionStart="FIGURES 36–41" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[187,1399,198,1903]" captionTargetId="figure-22@5.[172,1416,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 36–41. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 36. Genital capsule, lateral view; 37. Female seventh sternite, ventral view; 38. First valvula, lateral view; 39. Detail of sculptures of first valvula; 40. Second valvula, lateral view; 41. Detail of sculptures of second valaula." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500921" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500921/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Figs. 38, 39</figureCitation>
). Second valvulae with some distal teeth occupying about half of the total length (
<figureCitation id="BEAD2A3C290B3272FDE62D29FD1CD9E9" box="[527,664,1652,1678]" captionStart="FIGURES 36–41" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[187,1399,198,1903]" captionTargetId="figure-22@5.[172,1416,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 36–41. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 36. Genital capsule, lateral view; 37. Female seventh sternite, ventral view; 38. First valvula, lateral view; 39. Detail of sculptures of first valvula; 40. Second valvula, lateral view; 41. Detail of sculptures of second valaula." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500921" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6500921/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Figs. 40, 41</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="262936B9290B3272FF2E2DC5FC4DD9D4" blockId="1.[151,1437,1292,1930]" box="[199,969,1688,1715]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">
<emphasis id="14E2EAAB290B3272FF2E2DC5FEF7D9D5" bold="true" box="[199,371,1688,1714]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Measurement.</emphasis>
Length (including tegmen): 
<specimenCount id="3090FD30290B3272FD472DC5FD45D9D4" box="[686,705,1688,1715]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
5.6 mm, 
<specimenCount id="3090FD30290B3272FCCF2DC5FCB0D9D4" box="[806,820,1688,1715]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
5.7–5.9 mm.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
